Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:03.90,Dates,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,900)}September 10th (Fri)
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.40,0:00:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the real deal results.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the readers came through after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H525253&\frz-12.8\fax-0.22\blur0.869\fnBakuShinn\fs73.537\pos(333.333,381.056)}Colorfusical
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When Fukuda and the others came in \Nto complain, I had to stand up to them,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.68,0:00:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but to be honest, I didn't want \Nsomeone like Koji to beat us either.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.98,0:00:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would have just made it worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.69,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that the battle for the "Golden \NFuture Cup" is down to three entries.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kiyoshi Knight."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.28,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hideout Door."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shady Detective Trap."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.91,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you see the blue bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.91,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,aozora tobikau Blue Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:09.13,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,fluttering through the blue sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:09.13,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,ano tori ga miemasu ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:17.05,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happiness can't be described by a visible color, but I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:17.05,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shiawase wa itsumo mienai Color kanjiteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:22.68,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1800)}Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:34.57,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the inside of the sleeve of the shirt you gave me,
