Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:42.62,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,the word "FIGHT!" was embroidered in white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:42.62,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shiroi shishuu de tsuzurareta "FIGHT!" no gomoji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:51.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even though I tried so hard by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:51.09,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mou hitori demo ganbareru ki de ita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:59.43,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,890)}I wonder why my tears still fall?
