Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.35,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,Your love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:10.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll entrust myself to the wind since we are connected
