Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I saw it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.667,200.556)\c&HC1C6CC&\blur0.869\b1}Editorial Department
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.667,367.685)\c&H9CA1A8&\blur0.869\b1}Shounen Jack
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.667,548.185)\c&H808489&\blur0.869\b1}Jack Square
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.00,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.00,0:12:14.63,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the quality would be as good \Nas it was in the "Golden Future Cup,"
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.76,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but the feeling and the power \Nare even better than before.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.88,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Is tolerating all this guys back talk \Nfor so long finally going to pay off?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you grinning about?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're creeping me out.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So how is my name?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the editor, so do your job properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Fukuda,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't be talking to me\N like that before we even start—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about that right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.26,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you thought I'd be satisfied with just the \N"Golden Future Cup," then you were wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm betting everything on this!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll push my way past all the popular series!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get serialized this time around!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In {\i1}that{\i0} case, then let me just say this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.79,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have nothing to say about the art
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the story's metaphors and allegorical \Nsetting give it even more depth than before.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.65,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Aoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with this for the first chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can use chapter two to pull in—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.51,0:13:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not bad" means that it's also not great, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.59,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki, you're just reading too \Nmuch into the words he—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are any places I can \Nmake better, please tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.07,0:13:29.58,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I had thought losing the "Golden Future \NCup" would have wounded her pride, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The line in panel four on the second page could—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we couldn't end the \Nsecond chapter in 25 pages.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we did, we needed 27 pages
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to get the case solved in only one chapter.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The story is good, so we'll go with this.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll make sure to do the next one right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make sure to fix more \Nthan just what we were told to.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's on to chapter three.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.85,0:14:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be talking to Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.95,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you can.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.62,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should at least tell him \Ncongratulations directly at a time like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Mashiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,T—This is Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.19,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize for what I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.89,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.02,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That manga magazine on your bookshelf.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that have anything to do with \Nwhy you've been so out of it lately?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—You can't just go through your \Ndaughter's room without asking.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ashirogi Muto."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dreams are in there too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kaya tell you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you know about—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I figured out who you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I—It's not like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho, are you actually meeting him?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not meeting the guy you like?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird for a mom to be \Nsaying something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us aren't like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if we were, it's nobody else's business.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.38,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just worried you were \Ndoing the same thing that I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.35,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in middle school, \Nthere was a boy that I really liked.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.02,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it ended after years of only being \Nable to send letters back and forth.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Only letters—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.90,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't meet for a long time,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.95,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you think you might think the \Nother person isn't interested anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never think that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I did,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always believe in him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.93,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.98,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)\pos(600,123.676)\fs53.481\blur1.003\frz15\fax0.1\c&H767478&}Miyoshi Kaya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.98,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)\pos(626.667,193.87)\fs53.481\blur1.003\frz16\fax0.08\c&H767478&}Request
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.98,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)\pos(353.333,558.213)\fs60.167\blur1.003\frz18.5\fax0.03\c&H808080&}Can you give me Mashiro's\N\Ncellphone number
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, this is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll take it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.51,Dates,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,900)}December 8th (Wed)
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me in the usual cafe.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.15,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure {\i1}are{\i0} working hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida, I have something I'd like to ask you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, ask me anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter three is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll submit these for the meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do now is wait \Nfor the higher-ups' decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done all we can.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to the results!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to back them up \Nin the serialization meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Back them up?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.62,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure somebody is going to ask if they'll be \Nable to keep up the pace while still in school.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.26,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're pretty confident.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know if they'll get that far.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it would end like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only submitting the first \Nthree chapters for the meeting,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but they already have 10 finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.74,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They also have five manuscripts that they did \Nin two weeks each in case they got serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was all while they were also \Nworking on the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They really did all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in a position where\N I can go to the meetings yet,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.65,0:18:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so the best I can do is ask you to say they have \Nwhat it takes to do this while still in high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.03,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure everybody knows \Nhow much work they've done.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.83,Notebook,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H7B7B7C&\blur0.869\frz136\fax-0.15\pos(546.667,481.333)}Shady Detective Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.83,Notebook,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H8C8C8E&\blur0.869\frz136\fax-0.1\pos(620,411.139)}Serialization Name Chapter 2
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.83,Notebook,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H898989&\blur0.869\frz140\fax-0.2\pos(752,394.426)}Ashirogi Muto
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.62,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.61,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So this is screentone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.90,Entries,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,950)}Night before the Serialization Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.90,Entries,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,950)}December 15th (Wed)
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are working late today.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not actually working.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.85,0:20:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really trying to Fukuda serialized this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nakai has a good shot as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So just in case, I'm looking for assistants for Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.07,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I went around collecting examples from three \Npeople with good enough drawings to fill the spots.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, I don't care who it \Nis as long as they can draw well.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the names being submitted \Nfor the serialization meeting, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.93,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a total of 13 series \Nbeing submitted this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi sure got some good feedback.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.53,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it feels like most of it \Nis talking about future prospects.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you want to go grab a drink?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than just sitting \Naround here worrying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four veterans with submissions this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.57,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At best, there'll probably only \Nbe one newcomer chosen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think there could be two.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.28,0:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And after looking at the names, there might \Neven be a total of five new series chosen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way they'll choose five!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.35,0:21:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happened before with series like \N"Rookies" and "Hunter X Hunter."
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a crazy story from before \Nwe started working there!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.74,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's usually two new stories at most.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.73,0:21:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.59,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to get Ashirogi Muto serialized!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's got nothing to do with me wanting credit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the same boat, y'know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.30,0:21:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I really want to get to the point \Nwhere I can be part of those meetings.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure look like fun, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they do.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, this is the first time we've \Ngone drinking just the two of us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.37,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.75,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.39,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This time—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll get this series serialized—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.02,0:22:17.98,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.54,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,No, I guess it's already today.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.15,0:22:25.91,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.70,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,My future.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.95,0:22:32.33,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,With Shuujin—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.87,0:22:33.96,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.79,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\move(566.667,300.833,517.333,300.833)\fs50.139\blur1.003\frz8.5\fax0.06\c&HB09870&}Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.79,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\move(650,203.23,600.667,203.23)\fs46.796\blur1.003\frz8.5\fax0.08\c&HA99668&}Mashiro Moritaka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.79,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\move(533.333,552.196,484,552.196)\fs35.431\blur1.003\frz9.3\fax0.03\c&H968452&}Tomorrow is the Serialization Meeting.\NWe'll make sure to pass it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can say from the bottom of my heart that I'm glad I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,deaete yokatta to kokoro kara ieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are multiplying little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hito ga sukoshi zutsu fuete ku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While clenching their warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono nukumori wo kamishimenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could support each other or face the boring things head on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sasae attari hikutsu wo butsuke attari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally arrive at that place alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hitori ja tadori tsukenai basho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}We're now proceeding en route
